== 制作 ==
该剧包括“婆媳关系、丈夫出轨、[[第三者_(愛情)|小三]]挑战”等现代生活矛盾。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.enorth.com.cn/system/2013/03/10/010723265.shtml|title=《贤妻》热播引观众热议|access-date=2013-05-26|date=2013-03-10|work=北方网|archive-date=2019-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190824190227/http://news.enorth.com.cn/system/2013/03/10/010723265.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

该剧播出之后，不断被网友吐槽。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://cq.people.com.cn/newscenter/cq/news.cqr300?Num=7314032|title=电视剧《贤妻》热播受质疑保剑峰称看完戏就不会骂他了|access-date=2013-05-26|date=2013-03-20|work=人民网|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304083240/http://cq.people.com.cn/newscenter/cq/news.cqr300?Num=7314032|archivedate=2016-03-04}}</ref>[[西部网|西部网]]刊登刘运喜的文章《“贤妻”这部电视剧到底宣扬了什么》，称该剧“否定了[[社会主义|社会主义]][[精神文明|精神文明]]建设”。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.cnwest.com/content/2013-03/27/content_8814683_2.htm |title=《贤妻》这部电视剧到底宣扬了什么 |access-date=2013-05-26 |date=2013-03-27 |work=西部网 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304193118/http://news.cnwest.com/content/2013-03/27/content_8814683_2.htm |archive-date=2016-03-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

